reviewText: Moves too fast. They won't refund your money if you don't like it ( and I don't).

Very nicely done, and at times the movements are beautiful. Its easy to do, and has a flowing nature.
Linda is very supportive, and is well versed in the challenges of Parkinsons. The first time I did this I
slept better and felt better when I woke up. I like the review of movements she does at the end. She
keeps it interesting. I can see most with parkinsons would be able to do this. Peace to all with these
challenging symptoms.
